project_descr: The overarching objective is that the Government of Indonesia and target sub-national governments have access to and use quality real-time "big data" to inform policy making, planning and budgeting.

outputs.output_descr: The activity will lead to better service delivery through more effective feedback loops between citizens and governments. Capacity of local authorities to understand and use data to gather new insights will be developed.
